name: Hacker News App for Android
body:
### Hacker News App
This Application is developed for teach and build an basic Application for Hacker News in SDK 23 Android. This App has the following libraries:

* [Retrofit](http://square.github.io/retrofit/)
* [Event Bus](https://github.com/greenrobot/EventBus)
* [Gson](https://github.com/google/gson)
* [OkHttp](http://square.github.io/okhttp/)
* [Pretty Time](https://github.com/ocpsoft/prettytime)

### Support or Contact
